text: Q, Karl Marx said religion is the opiate of the masses. I say social media is the opiate of the masses.
1. The FBI had a search warrant. 2. A judge approved the search warrant. 3. No office was “broken into” 4. The subject of search said the FBI was professional and courteous.
This is why I sold out my $MJ at $31. Spot prices likely moving much lower as supply (and low entry barriers) overwhelm demand.
Karl Marx said religion was the opiate of the masses. Today social media is the opiate of the masses.
